					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dialogue between the players and Cora Highberry in the Serial Killer situation. Appears when Roger is dead (before or after Dolor appears). There are the first victims. A flag mark the dialogue happens before Dolor appears and other flag if Dolor is killed."
